I received the request from a user for the option to move attachments from one page to another when they cut and paste a part of a page to another page and the part of the page they are cutting contains (links to) attachments.

This should obviously not be the default, since often you just want to copy/cut the content without the attachments, but having the option would be a serious improvement for pages that are huge, with lots of attachments, and need to be split up into multiple pages.

This would probably be technically challenging to implement, but I'm throwing it out there in case more people are interested.

